
Overview of noun helper

The noun helper has 2 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                         
1. (1) assistant, helper, help, supporter -- (a person who contributes to the fulfillment of a need or furtherance of an effort or purpose; "my invaluable assistant"; "they hired additional help to finish the work")
2. (1) benefactor, helper -- (a person who helps people or institutions (especially with financial help))
